{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-post-container-index-tsx","path":"/post/etc/shadow-animation-afterimage/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h3>1. 이게 뭐야!</h3>\n<p>분명히 PC로 확인할 땐 별 문제가 없었는데, 모바일로 확인해 보니 애니메이션이 발생할 때 그림자의 잔상이 남는 것을 확인했다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/886cf971-2f9e-499e-aa3b-bc2d7a26fe3f/image.gif\" alt=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/e9eb95d1-5b86-4e4a-8d9f-d85fdc808e6d/image.gif\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h3>2. 해결 방법</h3>\n<p>열심히 구글링 해 보았지만 마땅한 해결 방법이 나오지 않아 결국 챗지피티의 도움을 받았다.\n결과적으로 아래 코드 두 줄을 추가하면 위와 같은 에러는 해결된다!</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">backface-visibility: hidden</code> 요소의 뒷면이 화면에 표시되지 않게 한다. 즉, 뒷면이 화면에 표시되지 않게 하여 잔상이 줄어들게 한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">transform: translateZ(0)</code> 3D 변형을 적용하여 GPU 가속을 강제로 사용하도록 한다. 이를 통해 애니메이션 동작이 더 부드럽게 처리되며, 잔상이 줄어들게 하는 효과가 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">drop-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0px 0px 11px <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>106<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 123<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.49<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token property\">backface-visibility</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hidden<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">translateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>3. 결과</h3>\n<p>잔상이 사라진 채로 잘 동작한다!\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/be2a560d-2d3b-4a39-8298-bb323db8c1f5/image.gif\" alt=\"\"></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"모바일 환경에서 애니메이션 사용 시 잔상이 생길 때","summary":"모바일 환경에서 애니메이션이 동작할 때 잔상이 생긴다면 어떻게 해결해야 할까?","date":"June 28, 2023","categories":["post","etc"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/59d3c1b4a82d28ed2c2afadedc15d35b/a0287/shadow-animation-afterimage.png","srcSet":"/static/59d3c1b4a82d28ed2c2afadedc15d35b/6ecb6/shadow-animation-afterimage.png 30w,\n/static/59d3c1b4a82d28ed2c2afadedc15d35b/43a9d/shadow-animation-afterimage.png 60w,\n/static/59d3c1b4a82d28ed2c2afadedc15d35b/a0287/shadow-animation-afterimage.png 120w,\n/static/59d3c1b4a82d28ed2c2afadedc15d35b/f5f72/shadow-animation-afterimage.png 240w","sizes":"(min-width: 120px) 120px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/59d3c1b4a82d28ed2c2afadedc15d35b/2b147/shadow-animation-afterimage.webp 30w,\n/static/59d3c1b4a82d28ed2c2afadedc15d35b/caa3b/shadow-animation-afterimage.webp 60w,\n/static/59d3c1b4a82d28ed2c2afadedc15d35b/b15f9/shadow-animation-afterimage.webp 120w,\n/static/59d3c1b4a82d28ed2c2afadedc15d35b/b5014/shadow-animation-afterimage.webp 240w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 120px) 120px, 100vw"}]},"width":120,"height":120}},"publicURL":"/static/59d3c1b4a82d28ed2c2afadedc15d35b/shadow-animation-afterimage.png"}}}}]},"file":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/bbf83/profile-image.jpg","srcSet":"/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/a8e5a/profile-image.jpg 30w,\n/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/bea51/profile-image.jpg 60w,\n/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/bbf83/profile-image.jpg 120w,\n/s